public abstract class JenaContainerAdaptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements RDFContainer

Adaptor class for the Jena implementations of the RDF Containers. Provides common methods for the RDF Container implementations.

See Also:
JenaBag, JenaSeq, JenaAlt
